casebody.data:
No. 10-8050. Richard Mills, Petitioner v. John Lempke, Superintendent, Five Points Correctional Facility. 562 U.S. 1211, 131 S. Ct. 1503,

179 L. Ed. 2d 294,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1221. February 22, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
